{"tid":2304990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1名懲教確診！張竹君：探病時感染 (唔肯答同邊個CASE 有關連)","createTime":"2020-11-29T09:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T09:43:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4389fb4008decba9928b898d554dbd5f69834a28","tid":2304990,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: LIVE現場"},{"pid":"bcd664b270698743c99d94097bd9c584cce344df","tid":2304990,"uid":281417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:15:59.000Z","msg":"建興<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec511c68082cbbeb3bccae2beb6b73bdade0c95","tid":2304990,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"懲教狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fdef62ec4ce9f418857f7877957325d2b1faadd","tid":2304990,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">勵敬懲教所人員初步確診 <br />\n職員及在囚人士檢測呈陰性</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562619-20201129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562619-20201129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=c21fbcff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562619-20201129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=acbf4588\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562619-20201129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n勵敬懲教所一名更生事務組懲教人員初步確診新型肺炎。<br />\n  <br />\n懲教署表示，這名懲教人員最近一次上班是在本月24日，同日獲通知，她早前休假期間，在外間醫院探病的病房，有病人確診，這名懲教人員被介定為密切接觸者。她其後在竹篙灣檢疫中心接受檢疫，昨晚獲通知初步確診。她最近沒有外遊紀錄，工作期間佩戴外科口罩，並與接觸人士保持適當社交距離，上班期間一直有進行體溫探測，體溫正常。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署表示，署方得悉該名懲教人員要入住檢疫中心後，已即時安排院所內所有在囚人士，以及有密切接觸職員進行病毒檢測，全部樣本測試結果均為陰性。院所已徹底清潔消毒相關地方，並會安排院所內所有職員及在囚人士再次進行病毒檢測。"}]}